Gun Runner - Kick Off
Out in the patrol car, Beth and Will are forced to a halt when a box of fireworks explodes in front
of them. They chase teenager Jason Patterson who admits that he stole the fireworks from his stepdad,
Ryan Fuller's garage. Concern grows when they realise that Fuller is at a football derby at Millwall
- with the rest of the fireworks.
